high_descs: Walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the tub.
Pick up the dirty black rag out of the tub.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, the hang a left and walk up to the left sink.
Put the dirty black rag in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean rag.
Walk back over to the tub.
Put the clean rag in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag in the tub.

high_descs: Turn around to face the tub.
Pick up the dirty black rag in the tub.
Bring the rag to the left sink next to the toilet.
Wash the rag in the left sink.
Bring the rag back to the tub on the left.
Put the rag in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag in the tub.

high_descs: move to the tub to the right
pick up a rag from the tub
move to the sink to the right
clean the rag in the sink
move to the sink to the left of you
put the rag in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag in the tub.
